Author: paleairity
Text: I feel this hardcore! I’ve been waiting to get my DECAYING wisdom tooth pulled for 6 weeks and my dentist didn’t think it was an issue at the time.   Well, it’s impacted and decided four weeks ago to shove my teeth out of the way and come in more. I went to the ER after passing out from pain. Dentist couldn’t set an earlier appointment.   I’ve been liquid fasting for 4 weeks, add in 3+ weeks more after my tooth is pulled-aaaaaaa dentists are a pain in the butt you have all of my sympathy.  Fasting is about our only bright side at this point
